        0001-ARM-toolchain-fixes.patch
        0002-Fix-ARM-skia-ICE.patch
        0003-bind-gen-Support-single_process-flag-in-generate_bin.patch
        0004-Run-blink-bindings-generation-single-threaded.patch)
